p.e:
HE TRICKED ME!
I READ FROM THE BOOK AND I
HAD NO CHOICE BUT TO FOLLOW
THE PROCEDURE.
MY QUESTIONS WENT UNANSWERED
AS HE WAS SO STOIC.

NOW... I FEEL DIFFERENT.
THE AIR SEEMS TO HAVE A CHILL.

I AM SEEING THINGS IN TOWN I
DIDN'T NOTICE BEFORE.

AND MAGICK...


                  IS REAL.

--A.W.
